The library of models for immature mosquitoes: 

+ "trivial" -- The trivial model 

+ ["basicL"](basicL.qmd) in [`ramp.xds`](https://dd-harp.github.io/ramp.xds/reference/dLdt.basicL.html) - The model `basicL` is an implementation of a model published by [@SmithDL2013MosquitoPopulation], generalized slightly to include density-dependent maturation rates.
